Introduction:

This is a coding challenge for the project "".

Documents:

It contains:

ModetoXML.java which contains code for converting *.modes to xml file
XMLtoMode.java which contains code for converting modes.xml to *.modes


Requirement : 

Java 1.6 or higher version should be installed in the system.

Usage:

Run the run.sh with the following arguments:
First argument should be mode
	-modetoxml for converting *.modes to xml file"
	-xmltomode for converting modes.xml to *.modes
Second argument should be <Path of the language pair directory>
Third argument should be <Path of the output dictionary for modes.xml>
	e.g. bash run.sh -xmltomode apertium-hin test
